(43, 7, 7, 62, 4, 5, 5, 'the world cannot hate you', 'Connection of Worldly Reception', 'Both passages emphasize the relationship between the world and those who testify to its evil. John 7:7 highlights the world''s hatred for Jesus due to His testimony, while 1 John 4:5 indicates that those of the world speak in ways the world accepts.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
