(43, 7, 10, 30, 5, 13, 13, 'not openly, but as it were in secret', 'Silence in Evil Times', 'This connection highlights the theme of discretion in challenging circumstances. Both passages emphasize the need for caution and silence in times perceived as evil or dangerous.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 7, 10, 40, 10, 16, 16, 'as it were in secret', 'Wisdom in Secrecy', 'This connection highlights the theme of being cautious and strategic in one''s actions. In John 7:10, Jesus goes to the feast ''as it were in secret,'' while Matthew 10:16 advises being ''wise as serpents'' in a hostile environment.', 'theme', 0.33499999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 7, 10, 23, 42, 2, 3, 'as it were in secret', 'Connection of Secrecy and Gentleness', 'This connection highlights the theme of subtlety in both passages. John 7:10 mentions Jesus going up ''in secret,'' while Isaiah 42:2-3 describes a gentle approach, emphasizing quietness and care.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 7, 10, 19, 26, 8, 8, NULL, 'Connection of Worship and Secrecy', 'This connection highlights the theme of reverence for God''s house. In John 7:10, Jesus goes to the feast in secret, while Psalms 26:8 expresses love for the habitation of God''s house, suggesting a deep respect for sacred spaces.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 7, 10, 19, 40, 8, 8, NULL, 'Connection of Will and Action', 'This connection highlights the theme of obedience to God''s will. In John 7:10, Jesus acts in secret, suggesting a deliberate choice to fulfill his mission, while Psalms 40:8 expresses a delight in doing God''s will, indicating a heart aligned with divine purpose.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 7, 10, 40, 3, 15, 15, NULL, 'Fulfillment of Righteousness', 'This connection highlights the theme of Jesus acting in accordance with divine purpose. In both passages, Jesus engages in significant actions—going to the feast in secret and fulfilling righteousness through baptism—demonstrating his commitment to God''s plan.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
